    We've heard a lot on this show about designers becoming builders using tools like v0 (https://v0.dev/) and today we get to do a deep dive with Pranathi Peri (https://x.com/pranathiperii) who is leading the design of v0 at Vercel. We discuss:

    • How Pran thinks about the design language of v0
    • Pran’s personal experiments using 3D and physics
    • Why Pran wants to bring “onboarding roulette” to v0
    • How Pran showed potential without having extensive experience
    • What it’s like collaborating with engineers like ShadCN and Rauno
    • + a lot more
    • Manuel (  / mamuso  ) is the VP of Design at Vercel
    • We discuss what it’s like collaborating with Shadcn (https://x.com/shadcn)
